-[10 Micro-Lecture Videos on Semantics by the Virtual Linguistics Campus](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLRIMXVU7SGRJnARkQhb6LO8KOi5rQf2Qn)

-[14 Videos on Semantics by the Virtual Linguistics Campus](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLRIMXVU7SGRJF8gxD70oZPBoFAYxGs4QL)

-[Linguistics as a Window to Understanding the Brain](http://www.floatinguniversity.com/lectures-pinker)

-[Lenguaje, lengua y habla](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B02Kh-DLnkc)

-[Introducción a fonética y fonología](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aMb7wNTCE3k)

-[Language. CrashCourse](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s9shPouRWCs)

