-[How language transformed humanity](http://www.ted.com/talks/mark_pagel_how_language_transformed_humanity)

-[What our language habits reveal](http://www.ted.com/talks/steven_pinker_on_language_and_thought)

-[The linguistic genius of babies](http://www.ted.com/talks/patricia_kuhl_the_linguistic_genius_of_babies)

-[Could your language affect your ability to save money?](http://www.ted.com/talks/keith_chen_could_your_language_affect_your_ability_to_save_money)

-[Txtng is killing language. JK!!!](http://www.ted.com/talks/john_mcwhorter_txtng_is_killing_language_jk)

-[A word game to communicate in any language](http://www.ted.com/talks/ajit_narayanan_a_word_game_to_communicate_in_any_language)

-[A Rosetta Stone for a lost language](http://www.ted.com/talks/rajesh_rao_computing_a_rosetta_stone_for_the_indus_script)

-[Don't insist on English!](http://www.ted.com/talks/patricia_ryan_ideas_in_all_languages_not_just_english)

-[Don't kill your language](http://www.ted.com/talks/suzanne_talhouk_don_t_kill_your_language)

-[Why is "X" the unknown](http://www.ted.com/talks/terry_moore_why_is_x_the_unknown)

-[History and Geography of Languages](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rYuPFpckHUc)

-[Theories of Language and Cognition](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RgvmKfvCwps)

-[Theories of Language Development (Nativist, Learning, Interactionist)](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RRGwdfQV8kU)

-[Language and the brain: Aphasia and split-brain patients](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lBqShvm4QRA)

-[What is Aphasia?](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P-xLbPsYdv0)

