#Recommended books
These are books recommended by students. 

-[*An Introduction to Language*](http://www.amazon.com/Introduction-Language-Victoria-Fromkin/dp/1133310680/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&qid=1428019043&sr=8-3&keywords=fromkin) - Dr. Victoria Fromkin



-[How Language Works (edition 3.0) by Michael Gasser](http://www.indiana.edu/~hlw/book.html)   Free online introductory linguistics textbook. 


